    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/e76a6aa0e5de1d951854a5303ba69628.poster.avif?t=1730983167\" width=620 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/e76a6aa0e5de1d951854a5303ba69628.webm?t=1730983167\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/e76a6aa0e5de1d951854a5303ba69628.mp4?t=1730983167\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沉浸入《雷鸣风暴》的游戏世界。在这里，四个王国为了争夺统治权而不断厮杀。你需要创建出最强牌组，在实时战役中与其他玩家对决。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/1f2f19348cb38f0c9797ad27d5aa8755.avif?t=1730983167\" width=620 height=248 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新颖的游戏机制结合了卡牌收集游戏与战术棋盘游戏的元素。从手中出牌放到棋盘上，看着你的战队直捣敌方基地！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/c9bf76d20bc2789ff74c109639d1579e.avif?t=1730983167\" width=620 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在四个王国中选择一个，创建最强的牌组，充分发挥出部队与法术的优势。随着环境因素的不断变化，你能否创建出能打败对手的终极牌组？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/01fe7019e3d7ebf32bace866ab702511.avif?t=1730983167\" width=620 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与全球各地的玩家对决。通过游戏内的表情文字祝贺胜出的对手，或者在对手面前把棋盘扫空。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/e4398583bbfde25c3b5d1b39fb849feb.avif?t=1730983167\" width=620 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《雷鸣风暴》独特的游戏机制结合了棋牌游戏的布局意识与卡牌收集游戏的资源管理元素。你需要在游戏中去限制对手的选择范围，掌控棋盘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/790600/extras/13252aef0aa4a721a75e73713d6f54b5.avif?t=1730983167\" width=620 height=149 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收集数十张拥有独特强大能力的卡牌，打造你自己的牌组。布局是致胜的关键，而游戏中拥有无限的牌组可能。</p>",
